Package cards

cards is a group of utilities for operating on cards.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    Class that represents a card
    CardAnalizer
    Class that permits analyze one HandCards
    DebugDeck
    Class that represents a Card Deck, the deck is constructed from file
    Deck
    Class that represents a Card Deck with Cards of all possible combinations between CardValue and Suit Deck has always this cards
    HandCards
    Class that represent the 5 cards in the game, that are owned by the player.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CardValue
    enum type that represents possible values of a Card
    Suit
    enum type that represents possible suit of a Card
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EndOfDeck
    Exception to take of no more cards in Deck
    InvalidCard
    Exception to take of invalid Card Construction
